data.title: The Donna Summer Tribute Site
data.text:
In a world where the term "diva" is as overused as a MAC machine in an Atlantic City casino, DONNA SUMMER stands as a reminder of what true divadom is. She had talent, class, style and a stack of gold and platinum records that's the envy of Fort Knox - yet at heart she still remained an "Ordinary Girl."

Singer... songwriter... artist... author... legend...

and...

ROCK & ROLL HALL OF FAMER...

DONNA SUMMER
